  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Jake Power: Policeman is a game In which the player assumes the role of the policeman Jake Power. In the game the player gets to drive in a police car which can be upgraded with better parts like an engine, wheels and a siren. Other activities include climbing ladders to save a cat for an old lady and catching thieves by shining on them with Jake's flashlight.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Become A Crime-Fighting Hero!\n\nPlay as Jake, helping him fight crime and complete his missions. Patrol the streets, chase criminals, and save innocent people to become a city hero.\n\nUncover burglaries, and blow the whistle on criminals in fun mini-games that test your crime-fighting skills.\n\nInvestigate crime scenes, follow footprints, and take part in thrilling car chases to clear the streets of criminals.\n\nMake your police car bigger and better by adding new wheels, engines, and sirens.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
